graph TB
    subgraph "Kueue Component"
        Controller[kueue-controller-manager<br/>Deployment]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP]
        Visibility[Visibility Server<br/>8082/TCP]
        Metrics[Metrics Exporter<br/>8080/TCP]

        Controller -->|serves| Webhook
        Controller -->|serves| Visibility
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        ClusterQueue[ClusterQueue CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
        LocalQueue[LocalQueue CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
        Workload[Workload CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
        ResourceFlavor[ResourceFlavor CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
        AdmissionCheck[AdmissionCheck CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
        WorkloadPriority[WorkloadPriorityClass CRD<br/>kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1]
    end

    User[User/Application] -->|creates| Job[Kubernetes Job<br/>batch/v1]
    Job -->|intercepted by| Webhook
    Webhook -->|creates| Workload
    Controller -->|watches| Workload
    Controller -->|evaluates quota| ClusterQueue
    LocalQueue -->|maps to| ClusterQueue
    Workload -->|references| LocalQueue
    Workload -->|uses| ResourceFlavor
    Workload -->|requires| AdmissionCheck
    Workload -->|has| WorkloadPriority

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
        CertManager[cert-manager<br/>TLS Certificates]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    Controller -->|watches/updates| K8sAPI
    Webhook -->|TLS certs| CertManager
    Visibility -->|TLS certs| CertManager
    Metrics -->|scraped by| Prometheus

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        TFJob[TFJob<br/>Kubeflow]
        PyTorchJob[PyTorchJob<br/>Kubeflow]
        RayJob[RayJob<br/>Ray Operator]
        JobSet[JobSet<br/>jobset.x-k8s.io]
    end

    Webhook -->|intercepts| TFJob
    Webhook -->|intercepts| PyTorchJob
    Webhook -->|intercepts| RayJob
    Webhook -->|intercepts| JobSet

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Visibility fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Metrics fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Workload fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ClusterQueue fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style LocalQueue fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style TFJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PyTorchJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RayJob fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
